spec_data.Name: golang-github-google-go-cmp-unit-test-devel
spec_data.Description:
This package is intended to be a more powerful and safer alternative
to reflect.DeepEqual for comparing whether two values are semantically
equal.

This package contains unit tests for project
providing packages with github.com/google/go-cmp prefix.
